      </h1>
      <p>
        Using
        <a href="https://github.com/bbatsov/rubocop">RuboCop</a>
        , RefactorCop scans open source Ruby projects, allowing you to discover code that may benefit from your contribution.
      </p>
      <section class="project-discovery">
